        "latex": "Calculer $\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\sin n\\theta}{2^n}$ et\n\t     $\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\cos n\\theta}{n2^n}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\sin n\\theta}{2^n}\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\cos n\\theta}{n2^n}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7a2dd064-7570-4eb1-a81b-3e42e8e4becf",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\sin n\\theta}{2^n} =\n\t\t\\frac{2\\sin\\theta}{5-4\\cos\\theta}$,\\quad\n\t     $\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\cos n\\theta}{n2^n} =\n\t\t\\ln2 - \\frac12\\ln(5-4\\cos\\theta)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\sin n\\theta}{2^n} =\n        \\frac{2\\sin\\theta}{5-4\\cos\\theta}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\cos n\\theta}{n2^n} =\n        \\ln2 - \\frac12\\ln(5-4\\cos\\theta)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
